                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The dread wraith extends its hand toward another wraith creature within 100 feet. The target wraith dissolves and streaks toward the dread wraith in a straight line, dealing [[/r 6d10 #negative]] negative damage to each creature along the line (<span data-pf2-check=\"fortitude\" data-pf2-dc=\"28\" data-pf2-traits=\"wraith,damaging-effect\" data-pf2-label=\"Absorb Wraith DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">basic Fortitude</span> save).</p>\n<p>The dread wraith absorbs the essence of the target wraith, becoming @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Quickened]{Quickened} and gaining a +10-foot status bonus to its fly Speed for a number of rounds equal to the level of the absorbed wraith. It can use its extra action only to Fly or Strike.</p>\n<p>An unwilling target can attempt a <span data-pf2-check=\"will\" data-pf2-dc=\"28\" data-pf2-traits=\"wraith,damaging-effect\" data-pf2-label=\"Absorb Wraith DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Will</span> save to resist being absorbed.</p>"
                },
